&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Temporary Data Administrator (Fixed Term Contract)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Location: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Haringey &amp; Islington&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a temporary full time role offered on a Fixed term Contract From September to January each year&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Vaccination UK are the NHS commissioned provider of the School Aged Immunisation Programme in Dudley, Walsall, Wolverhampton, and 9 boroughs of North East London, we also deliver the Hertfordshire Fluenz programme for HCT.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit skilled and experienced Data administrators, capable of working quickly with 100% accuracy to ensure we meet deadlines.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The position of Schools Data Administrator is an integral role in a busy team. Your role is to support the Haringey and Islington teams with the inputting of child immunisation data in the correct format and submit them to the correct point of contact. You will also keep up to date figures for use in invoicing and data audits, as well as completing regular data quality checks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Main Responsibilities will be:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Inputting large amounts of child health data to the highest degree of accuracy&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Working in Excel to present and organise the data&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Working with other team members to ensure all data is collected correctly&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Organising and preparing all paper records that have been submitted into clearly marked boxes ready for storage&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Working quickly to meet daily deadlines&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Calculating figures to be used in invoicing and data analysis&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Support management by performing data audits and writing reports to analyse findings&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Thoroughly check all data to identify and correct inconsistencies&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Other tasks dependent on business needs such as triaging consent forms&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you have no working experience in this area but have recently graduated, then we would still like to hear from you&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job Types: Full-time, Temporary&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Salary: £10.00 /hour inclusive&lt;/p&gt;
